Dialogue: 9,0:00:07.82,0:00:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Não, três!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:09.36,0:00:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,O gás está muito denso.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:11.15,0:00:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Análise de imagem completa.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:13.21,0:00:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Vou colocar na tela principal.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:16.16,0:00:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:17.48,0:00:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso é um tipo humanoide?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:19.31,0:00:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Processando imagem.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:22.33,0:00:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Não... Isso é...
