Dialogue: 9,0:02:10.98,0:02:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Contato visual com o alvo.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:13.44,0:02:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Q-Que é isso—
Dialogue: 9,0:02:18.11,0:02:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}702...
Dialogue: 9,0:02:19.49,0:02:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Foi a Gauna que devorou os Garde de Hoshijiro.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:24.45,0:02:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,É só placenta!
Dialogue: 9,0:02:25.91,0:02:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Não pense nisso!
Dialogue: 9,0:02:33.21,0:02:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Os Gaunas inimigos se dispersaram.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:35.46,0:02:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,O esquadrão de Samari pega o G489.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:37.17,0:02:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,O de Nakazono leva o G490.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:39.01,0:02:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,O de Kunato pega o G491.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:40.84,0:02:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Foque no seu alvo.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:42.85,0:02:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Espere que o inimigo tenha armas.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:44.47,0:02:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:45.47,0:02:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Todas as unidades, dispersar.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:48.02,0:02:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Todos os esquadrões se dispersaram\Nem direção ao alvo.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:51.31,0:02:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Formação 122A.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:53.27,0:02:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Honoka Ren e Hou vão imobilizá-lo\Ncom seus canhões Heigus.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:56.94,0:02:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze vai me dar suporte.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:58.90,0:02:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:09.71,0:03:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Ai...
Dialogue: 9,0:03:10.62,0:03:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso dói!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:12.58,0:03:15.25,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,Dói, dói!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:14.00,0:03:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,De onde vem essa voz?!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:16.21,0:03:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Olha esse rastro saindo do G491!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:20.22,0:03:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Os Gaunas estão usando o sinal de Hoshijiro!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:22.59,0:03:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}{\i1}Um piloto em um robô...{\i0}
Dialogue: 9,0:03:24.64,0:03:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eles estão emulando os Gardes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 9,0:03:26.39,0:03:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}{\i1}Ainda...{\i0}
Dialogue: 9,0:03:27.64,0:03:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele pode imitar qualquer coisa\Ne ainda seria um Gauna!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:30.44,0:03:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mantenham o ataque!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:32.02,0:03:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Todas as esquadras, relatório de status.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:34.02,0:03:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Falando Samari.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Estamos perseguindo o G489\Nem formação de linha.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:37.53,0:03:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Aqui é Nakazono!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:38.36,0:03:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Estamos engajando o G490.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:39.78,0:03:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,É rápido!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:41.07,0:03:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,G490 está corrompendo o quadro 139.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:44.41,0:03:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,As estacas placentárias perfuraram o quadro.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:51.37,0:03:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Aqui é Hoshijiro, relatando que o quadro foi destruído.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:53.08,0:03:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{bg}Quadro 138, dano severo!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,É... você... Hoshijiro?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:03.84,0:04:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshijiro!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:04.93,0:04:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:05.76,0:04:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Não avance!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:14.52,0:04:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Você consegue me ouvir?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:15.40,0:04:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshijiro!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:15.40,0:04:16.61,DefaultAlt,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:16.61,0:04:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Pare, Tanikaze!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:18.07,0:04:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles não entendem o que você está dizendo!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:20.61,0:04:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0...[T1][T2]Tanikaze[T3]...]
Dialogue: 9,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mensagem da Divisão de Exobiologia. {exobiology division, change typeset if you change it}
