Dialogue: 9,0:20:31.71,0:20:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos lá, Nagate!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:33.96,0:20:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Qual é o sentido disso?
Dialogue: 9,0:20:36.63,0:20:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Bem, você não quer animar a Hiyama {**-san}?
Dialogue: 9,0:20:39.84,0:20:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ela é sempre tão gentil conosco.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:41.63,0:20:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nós deveríamos retribuir o favor.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:45.30,0:20:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:55.48,0:20:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0...[T1]Lala[T2]...]
Dialogue: 9,0:20:59.90,0:21:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiro?
Dialogue: 9,0:21:01.03,0:21:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 9,0:21:02.53,0:21:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ser chamada pelo primeiro nome dela geralmente a deixa comicamente brava.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:08.78,0:21:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Hum... Eu...
Dialogue: 9,0:21:11.08,0:21:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Izana sugeriu que isso poderia te animar.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:18.46,0:21:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Chegue aqui, Izana!
Dialogue: 9,0:21:23.22,0:21:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, não!
Dialogue: 9,0:21:24.55,0:21:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Cola instantânea derramada!
Dialogue: 9,0:21:29.43,0:21:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Qual foi aquela voz?
Dialogue: 9,0:21:30.76,0:21:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Um animal?
Dialogue: 9,0:21:36.31,0:21:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Me desculpe, Hiyama{**-san}!
Dialogue: 9,0:22:00.04,0:22:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Mã...
Dialogue: 9,0:22:01.50,0:22:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Mamã...
Dialogue: 9,0:22:18.06,0:22:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0...[T1]Ta-ni-ka-ze[T2]...]
